{
  "id": "adv_card_ai_03_03",
  "title": "小美山愛 3話 しょっぱいチョコ",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――バレンタインイベント当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Day of Valentine's Day event",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stgae01",
      "startTime": 1.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_03-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、{user}さん！　お疲れ様です！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ {user}-san! Thanks for your help!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stgae01",
      "startTime": 6.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "結果、イベントに出ることになったし\n楽曲も間に合って良かったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As a result‚ I'm glad we're going to be\nat the event and we got the music in time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_03-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "はい。あの後、いろいろありましたけど……\n最後には、本音でこころとぶつかり合えました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. A lot has happened since then. ……\nWe were able to have a real heart-to-heart talk.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stgae01",
      "startTime": 18.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_03-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんが助けてくれたからです\n本当にありがとうございます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because {user}-san helped.\nThank you so much!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.5902398479,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stgae01",
      "startTime": 24.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "俺は何もしていないよ\n愛の頑張りがあったから、この日を迎えられたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I didn't do anything.\nIt was all thanks to Ai's hard work.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "それに今回は\n愛とこころのおかげでいい曲が出来たな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And this time‚\nthanks to Ai and Kokoro‚ we've got a great song.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.0433333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stgae01",
      "startTime": 35.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_03-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "え？　私はただ駆け回ってただけで……\n一番のお手柄は、こころです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh?　I was just running around……\nThe best of the best is Kokoro.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stgae01",
      "startTime": 41.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "でも、愛はずっとこころに寄り添って\n支えてあげていたんだろ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But you know‚ Ai has always been there\nand supported Kokoro.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.51,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "それに、振り付けには愛のアイデアが\n沢山採用されたとも聞いてるぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And I hear that a lot of Ai's ideas\nwere used in the choreography.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stgae01",
      "startTime": 52
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_03-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "そんな！　恐れ多いです！　たまたまですよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh no! I'm not!　It's just a coincidence!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stgae01",
      "startTime": 56.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さんと葵も、愛のダンスのセンスが\n開花し始めてるって褒めてたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio-san and Aoi also praised that Ai's dance sense\nis beginning to blossom.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stgae01",
      "startTime": 62.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_03-ai006.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さんと葵さんが！？\nえへへ、凄く嬉しいです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio-san and Aoi-san!?\nEhehe‚ I'm so happy!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stgae01",
      "startTime": 67.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "次の曲では、LizNoirのセンターを\n狙ってみてもいいんじゃないのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Maybe you can try to get\nLizNoir's center position in the next song?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stgae01",
      "startTime": 73.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_03-ai007.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そんな恐れ多いこと出来ませんよ！\n私は端っこが定位置ですから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can't do such a fearful thing!\nBecause I'm positioned at the edge!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_03-ai008.m4a",
      "text": "私までこころみたいに次期センター！\nとか言い出したら、収拾がつかなくなっちゃいます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don't think it's a good idea for me to do the\n\"The next center is me!\" like Kokoro always does.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stgae01",
      "startTime": 86.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_03-ai009.m4a",
      "text": "それに……私、自分のポジションに\n誇りを持ってるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And …… I take a lot of pride\nin my position.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "誇り？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Pride?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stgae01",
      "startTime": 93.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_03-ai010.m4a",
      "text": "はい。私が、LizNoirのセンターを\nみんなを輝かせる。それが私の誇りです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ I am. I will make the center of LizNoir shine for everyone.\nThat's what I'm proud of.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stgae01",
      "startTime": 102.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_03-ai011.m4a",
      "text": "だから、私はセンターじゃなくていいんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So I don't have to be the center.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stgae01",
      "startTime": 106.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_03-ai012.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さんを、葵さんを、そしてこころを――\nもっともっと輝かせたいんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio-san‚ Aoi-san‚ and Kokoro…\nI want them to shine brighter.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stgae01",
      "startTime": 113.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_03-ai013.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルの頂点に立つのは私じゃなくて\nLizNoirの四人ですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm not the one who will be at the top of the idol game.\nBut the four of us‚ LizNoir are going to.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stgae01",
      "startTime": 125.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_03-ai014.m4a",
      "text": "だから、私は、今の私のままでいいと思ってます\n……おかしいですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So I think I'm just fine the way I am.\nIs ……it weird?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stgae01",
      "startTime": 128.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "愛らしくていいと思う。……でもいつか\n愛が一番輝いている姿も見せてほしいな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think it's just so Ai….But\nI hope Ai will also show out yourself the brightest someday.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_03-ai015.m4a",
      "text": "……ふふっ、ありがとうございます\n考えておきます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…… Hehe‚ thank you!\nI will think about it!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stgae01",
      "startTime": 141.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_03-ai016.m4a",
      "text": "……最後に、{user}さん\n一つだけ、お願いしてもいいですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…… Finally‚ {user}-san\nMay I ask one more thing?",
        "id": ""
